onic athletes including gymnast Simone Biles, golfer Tiger Woods, and baseball star Babe Ruth in receiving the nation's highest civilian honor, the Medal of Freedom.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"other iconic athletes\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's highest civilian honor\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"the Medal\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"Freedom\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But between the excitement of the Olympics, Ledecky is a regular parishioner of the Church of the Little Flower in Bethesda, Maryland.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congressional_Country_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.248037941426792e-21, \"text\": \"Bethesda, Maryland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congressional_Country_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congressional_Country_Club\"}, {\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congressional_Country_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.248037941426792e-21, \"text\": \"Bethesda, Maryland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congressional_Country_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congressional_Country_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the excitement\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"a regular parishioner\", \"from\": 9